<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Impatiently" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Impatiently,</orth> passionately: <cit><quote>the current, being stopped, i. doth rage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.7.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 7, 26</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>i. I burn with thy desire,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 108</bibl></cit> (eagerly). <cit><quote>and too i. stamped with your foot,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.244" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 244</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>